result.adr_address: 40 Staunton St, Central, Hong Kong
result.name: Bocadito

reviews.text: The bartender vyoma is amazing. Only come there to have cocktails made by her.

Thank you for introducing nice cocktails.
It's a great experience and the price is cheap~ 😍

Stumbled across this place by accident and had a great time. The British girl tending the bar was great. Very knowledgeable on her drinks and the local area. Popped in for 1 and left after half a dozen a few hours later. Well worth a visit if in the area.
The drinks were not that great and the staff wasn't very pleasant. Also the bathroom door is messed up the sitting area stinks.
Solid "local" in Soho. Good service, cozy space and wide selection of spirits and decent draft beer
